BattleInit
   Set Ally starting position
   Set Enemy starting position
   Draw Battle screen/status information/sprites
BattleOrder
   Randomly select turn order, taking into account stats (eventually)
   Next character selects action and target
   Execute action (applying status effects)
CheckStatus
   Process negative status effects
   Hit point negation
   If character is critical, re-assign sprite (25%)
   If character is dead, re-assign sprite and remove them from the turn order and abort any actions they may have ordered
